cu.explanation_en: Setting SST to 999 exceeds the valid range for slice/service type (0-255), causing SNSSAI configuration errors.

du.explanation_en: Setting nrofDownlinkSymbols to 15 exceeds the valid range for TDD symbol configuration, causing frame structure errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 nrofDownlinkSymbols 設定為 15 超過 TDD 符號配置的有效範圍，會導致幀結構錯誤。
